attachments.title: 3D Printed Honeycomb Saves Bees Time and Energy
attachments.text: Most people have pretty strong opinions about bees. If you're allergic, it's perfectly understandable to want to avoid them at all costs. But in terms of the non-allergic population, most of us don't appreciate bees nearly enough.
